Name: Golem Foxen Box
Description:
Use to activate the mount: Golem Foxen.

Alternatively, you may visit the Kalista Counter at Meowlux Store (2F, Shopping Center near Pioneer Bureau) to exchange it for Meowlux Premium Cards.
